</taxonomicName>
is endemic to 
<collectingRegion id="49D4F84AFFBD9A60FC5FFA01787FFA78" box="[931,1063,1459,1485]" country="Philippines" name="Zamboanga" pageId="5" pageNumber="168">Zamboanga</collectingRegion>
Peninsula, Mindanao, where it is currently known in the provinces of 
<collectingRegion id="49D4F84AFFBD9A60FDD0FA647F4DFA45" box="[556,789,1494,1520]" country="Philippines" name="Zamboanga Sibugay" pageId="5" pageNumber="168">Zamboanga Sibugay</collectingRegion>
